DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a=random(2,10,1);

BEGIN_TEXT
For the function \( f(x)= $a e^x, \) calculate the following function values:
$BR
\(f(-3)=\) \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
\(f(-1)=\) \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
\(f(0)=\) \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
\(f(1)=\) \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
\(f(3)=\) \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
END_TEXT

$ans1 = $a*exp(-3);
$ans2 = $a*exp(-1);
$ans3 = $a;
$ans4 = $a*exp(1);
$ans5 = $a*exp(3);

ANS(num_cmp($ans1));
ANS(num_cmp($ans2));
ANS(num_cmp($ans3));
ANS(num_cmp($ans4));
ANS(num_cmp($ans5));

